text: Stocqueler is a surname. People with that name include: * Edwin Roper Loftus Stocqueler (1829-1895), British artist * Joachim Hayward Stocqueler (1801-1886), British journalist, author and lecturer with interests in the theatre and in Indian and military affairs * Giovanna Sestini (married name Joanna Stocqueler, 1749-1814), Italian-born soprano singer ==See also== *
